library(tidyverse)

prices = read_csv("/Users/alexanderkell/Documents/SGI/Projects/11-starter-kits/data/processed/starter-kits/Kenya/Results/MCAPrices.csv")

cols(

  commodity = [31mcol_character()[39m,
  region = [31mcol_character()[39m,
  prices = [32mcol_double()[39m,
  year = [32mcol_double()[39m

prices
prices_grouped = prices %>% group_by(commodity, year) %>% summarise(price = mean(prices))
`summarise()` regrouping output by 'commodity' (override with `.groups` argument)
prices_grouped
prices_grouped %>% ggplot() + geom_line(aes(x=year, y=price, color=commodity)) + theme_bw()



capacity = read_csv("/Users/alexanderkell/Documents/SGI/Projects/11-starter-kits/data/processed/starter-kits/Kenya/Results/MCACapacity.csv")

[36m[39m [1m[1mColumn specification[1m[22m [36m[39m
cols(
  technology = [31mcol_character()[39m,
  dst_region = [31mcol_character()[39m,
  region = [31mcol_character()[39m,
  agent = [31mcol_character()[39m,
  sector = [31mcol_character()[39m,
  type = [31mcol_character()[39m,
  year = [32mcol_double()[39m,
  capacity = [32mcol_double()[39m
)
head(capacity)
capacity_summed = capacity %>% group_by(technology, sector, year, agent) %>% summarise(capacity=sum(capacity))
`summarise()` regrouping output by 'technology', 'sector', 'year' (override with `.groups` argument)
head(capacity_summed)
ggplot(data=filter(capacity_summed, sector=="power"), aes(x=year, y=capacity, color=technology, linetype=agent)) + geom_line() + theme_classic()


ggplot(data=filter(capacity_summed, sector=="power"), aes(x=year, y=capacity, fill=technology)) + geom_bar(stat='identity', colour="black") + facet_grid(cols=vars(agent)) + theme_classic()
